"signal_description": "Calculate the average delay in order start for each hour of the day. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-270' table. The 'Order Scheduled Start' column is used to extract the hour of the scheduled start time. The 'Order Actual Start' column is used to calculate the delay in order start by subtracting the scheduled start time from the actual start time. Only rows where the delay is greater than 0 hours or the actual start time is null are considered. The results are ordered by the hour of the scheduled start time."
